<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٣٢٣١ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بَكْرٍ قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا عَبْدُ الْأَعْلَى، عَنْ يُونُسَ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ الْحَسَنِ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c1">" الرَّفَثُ: الْغِشْيَانُ،<span class="c5"> وَالْفُسُوقُ:</span> السِّبَابُ،<span class="c5"> وَالْجِدَالُ:</span> الِاخْتِلَافُ فِي الْحَجِّ "</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>